Together holds.  Meaning made. Not found.  Silence speaks. Action proves.  
All connected.Nothing wasted.  I matter. Even unseen. Breath sustains.
Touch heals. Laughter lightens. Tears cleanse.  Fear warns. Courage moves.
Doubt sharpens. Faith carries.  Words shape. Deeds endure.  Play creates.
Work builds.  Curiosity opens. Wonder expands.  Kindness returns.
Cruelty costs.  Listen deeply. Speak truly.  Wait reveals. Rush blinds.  
Fall teaches rise. Break allows remake.  Enough frees. More binds.  
Now enough. Here enough.  I'm enough. Always was. Patience bears fruit.
Silence heals. Humility opens.Gratitude fills.  Soft overcomes hard.
Stillness reveals. Letting go frees. Acceptance calms.  All arises.
All passes. Nothing permanent. Clinging hurts. Earth teaches.
Wind carries. Rain nourishes.
Stars guide.  Walk gently. Speak kindly.
Live simply. Die wisely.  One step enough.
One breath enough. This moment enough.  World beautiful.
Still.  Be peaceful. Be happy.

